 of the gate, and the group of magicians in the back room.  Got 2 shovels and 1 broom.  I traded a fire emerald for the torch from some other magician.  Now I'm prancing down there like a crazy lunatik looking for my pages, so far I've got earth and fire, and seen akkstaff numerous times (grrr)... My mage friend got his ass kicked down there at level 48 by linara parlone, I laughed at him.  He was running around with 2 bubs of health left and she dotted him and he died.  Just make sure you have lev on, or not fall down that hole <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Pet pathing around there is pretty bad.  <br>
<br>
I got most of the quest components from friends, like mermaid scales and fire drake scales, I got the toes off of gornit in OOT, I camped him with 2 other mages and we all got toes in 2-3 hours.  <br>
<br>
